    {
      "id": 380958,
      "category": "researcher",
      "content": "The PoC link was as follows - \n```\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/comm/mynetwork/discovery-see-all/?usecase=EMAIL_MIXED_RECOMMENDATIONS&entityUrn=urn:li:fs_DiscoveryEntity:(urn:li:member:<USER-ID>,PEOPLE_FOLLOW)&trk=eml-edge-discover&midToken=AQGOWzyQBc3Qug&midSig=0U3avif_ryOWI1&trkEmail=eml-email_edge_discover_01-recommended_edges-4-cta_pf-null-h3akrx~lgrx0iea~dl-null-neptune/mynetwork.discovery~see~all&lipi=urn:li:page:email_email_edge_discover_01;CJWMj7vwSYGntneNwUgFrQ==\n```\n\nHere `<USER-ID>` is the `fsd_profile` value that is publicly available. Using this crafted link it was possible to make any user on linkedin follow us once they click on it. ",
      "updated_at": "2023-12-06T18:12:24.535Z",
